{"tid":2242734,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"比國泰航空嘅疫市建議","createTime":"2020-10-14T08:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T08:55:29.000Z","uid":254330,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6df7899a9d6385159083f561c3df6ef629a70a02","tid":2242734,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"國泰由3月開始客運基本上冇生意做, cabin crew又冇得撈, 公司又冇錢賺, 股東又蝕到喊, 咁係呢個情況下可以點賺錢呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係學子公司UO咁搞flycation喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過國泰就當然要有番國泰特色, 就係空姐主題嘅flycation喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家諗諗, 國泰最本事係咩? 有好多架客運用飛機, 有好多employee等住開工<br />\n<br />\n咁國泰空姐最本事嘅副業係咩? 相信各位連登仔都有共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果國泰肯搞番個空姐主題嘅flycation, 係公海飛番幾個鐘, 我諗每個客收番2皮都唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好睇小香港嘅有錢人,1k飛個半鐘, 仲要係UO,都咁多人磅水, 呢個空姐主題收番2皮根本就不是問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一架B777可以載300幾人, 當social distance只可以載1/3都可以載100人呀, 如果first class/business class又可以賣貴d, 當然quality又可能好好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n粗略估計因航一轉net income 至少200萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反應熱烈又可以坐地起價<br />\n<br />\n空姐有工開, 有人工, 有貼士, 仲可能因為咁識番個有錢佬<br />\n國泰有錢袋, 膠層有花紅, 業績都靚好多<br />\n客人又有享受, 又可以飛番轉<br />\n<br />\ntriple win!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074b95416b531e3d606ef4ae13eae25624e5edbe","tid":2242734,"uid":98899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"2皮 笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246a821ac30bd690ab6dd3fc3ca7a9d3d59f08cd","tid":2242734,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"074b95416b531e3d606ef4ae13eae25624e